33 分，由武汉开往汕头的 G1175 次列车（两列动车组重联的动车组）在广州南站即将开车时，一名旅客（持广州南至汕尾的 10 号车厢车票）突然从该车 8 号车厢，下车跑向重联的另一列动车组 9 号车厢，扒阻正在关闭的车门，手指不慎被夹。 站台工作人员发现后，立即呼叫司机停车，并将旅客安置到站台安全地点，通知 120 医护人员到达现场。经初步检查，旅客手指夹伤，目前已送往医院接受进一步检查治疗。 铁路部门提醒，旅客在乘车时请勿阻挡列车车门关闭，强行上下车。 澎湃新闻记者 陈绪厚 实习生 汪健 本期编辑 邢潭 内容来源广州南站通报「高铁夹到乘客拖行」事件"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-f20c2b0aa688b120d54f1b9ac7236ebc_1440w.webp?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "587 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/7521165567"}}, "attached_info": "CkEIoar5psXot9wkEAMaCTExMjQ4MDgxNCC4yZ27BjAAOLIGQAJyCjc1MjExNjU1Njd4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "3_1734931318.846283", "card_id": "Q_6982007681", "card_label": {"type": "hot", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 298}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "车主花 200 万买仰望 U9，在租给租车公司后被暴力拆解，具体情况如何？车主应该如何维权？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "近日，一位比亚迪仰望 U9 车主在网上发视频维权。他花费 200 万元买的仰望 U9，被租赁公司出租后遭到租车人的暴力拆解，本人已报警维权。200 万买的仰望 u9 出租后被暴力拆解，车主：已报警"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-450a6df268d77f9ae67c3e18283b571d_1440w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "199 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/6982007681"}}, "attached_info": "CkEIoar5psXot9wkEAMaCTExMjM3MzE4MSD8l/66BjAAOJ8HQANyCjY5ODIwMDc2ODF4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "4_1734931318.846696", "card_id": "Q_7522834285", "card_label": {"type": "hot", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png", "night_ic